pageContext.claim: “Yeah, but media is more corrupt than Biden, and Biden's very corrupt. He's always been corrupt. He, everybody knew he was corrupt, but now we caught him, you know, very cold. But look what he did to General Flynn. Right? With the Logan Act.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump has no evidence to claim former vice president Joe Biden is "corrupt" or "crooked." Biden, unlike Trump, had disclosed decades of tax returns. Hunter Biden, one of his sons, did business deals that might not have come his way if he had not been a vice president's son, but the same could be said of Trump's adult children.  As for Flynn and the Logan Act, that claim is based on some cryptic after-the-fact notes taken by an FBI agent, while people in the room say Biden did not raise the Logan Act.
